00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:39,520
 koji je

994
00:35:39,520 --> 00:35:40,200
 evo,

995
00:35:40,200 --> 00:35:41,220
 doživio puno

996
00:35:41,220 --> 00:35:42,000
 izdanja,

997
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:43,580
 a vas svakako

998
00:35:43,580 --> 00:35:43,880
 evo,

999
00:35:43,880 --> 00:35:44,920
 potičem da ostanete

1000
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:45,760
 dalje na valovima

1001
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:47,320
 Hrvatskog katoličkog radija,

1002
00:35:47,560 --> 00:35:48,660
 a mi se vraćamo u studio

1003
00:35:48,660 --> 00:35:49,780
 nakon glazbenog predaha.

1004
00:35:49,780 --> 00:35:52,640
 Čuj brate,

1005
00:35:52,640 --> 00:35:53,520
 čuj sestro,

1006
00:35:53,520 --> 00:35:54,720
 gospodin je jedan

1007
00:35:54,720 --> 00:35:55,940
 koji te voli osobno,

1008
00:35:55,940 --> 00:35:57,680
 koji te voli tako kakav jesi,

1009
00:35:57,680 --> 00:35:59,360
 bez obzira kakvi smo,

1010
00:35:59,360 --> 00:36:01,580
 naš Bog je Bog ljubavi,

1011
00:36:01,580 --> 00:36:03,700
 zato večeras u ovoj emisiji

1012
00:36:03,700 --> 00:36:04,560
 smo razgovarali

1013
00:36:04,560 --> 00:36:05,700
 o našem divnom Bogu,

1014
00:36:05,700 --> 00:36:06,500
 a sada ćemo

1015
00:36:06,500 --> 00:36:08,080
 podkrijepiti kako to Bog

1016
00:36:08,080 --> 00:36:08,920
 djeluje i danas,

1017
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:10,860
 ali prije nego nastavimo

1018
00:36:10,860 --> 00:36:12,440
 sa ovim malim svjedočanstvom,

1019
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:14,580
 pišite nam kako vam se sviđa

1020
00:36:14,580 --> 00:36:15,760
 ova nova emisija

1021
00:36:15,760 --> 00:36:17,180
 Duhovno-duhovite večeri,

1022
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:18,400
 ovo je druga emisija

1023
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:19,700
 kako smo već na valovima

1024
00:36:19,700 --> 00:36:21,120
 Hrvatsko-katoličkog radija

1025
00:36:21,120 --> 00:36:22,720
 svakog utorka u 8 sati,

1026
00:36:22,720 --> 00:36:25,640
 naravno ovu emisiju

1027
00:36:25,640 --> 00:36:27,260
 moći ćete i pregledati

1028
00:36:27,260 --> 00:36:28,820
 na mojom Instagram profilu

1029
00:36:28,820 --> 00:36:29,800
 Frastijepan Brčina,

1030
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:31,080
 na Facebook profilu

1031
00:36:31,080 --> 00:36:32,660
 Hrvatsko-katoličkog radija,

1032
00:36:32,660 --> 00:36:33,920
 na YouTube kanalu

1033
00:36:33,920 --> 00:36:35,380
 Budi Frajer,

1034
00:36:35,380 --> 00:36:37,820
 tako da sve te društvene mreže

1035
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:40,420
 možete svakako zaviriti,

1036
00:36:40,420 --> 00:36:42,200
 pogledati, zapratiti, dijeliti.

1037
00:36:42,200 --> 00:36:43,820
 Vama svima još jednom

1038
00:36:43,820 --> 00:36:45,660
 lijep pozdrav koji nas pratite,

1039
00:36:45,660 --> 00:36:46,580
 koji nas slušate,

1040
00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:47,680
 koji komentirate

1041
00:36:47,680 --> 00:36:49,600
 i slobodno kritizirajte,

1042
00:36:49,600 --> 00:36:50,440
 pohvalite,

1043
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:51,780
 recite što mislite,

1044
00:36:51,780 --> 00:36:53,680
 svakako ćemo gledati

1045
00:36:53,680 --> 00:36:55,400
 da vas i osobno

1046
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:57,000
 uvažimo vaše komentare.

1047
00:36:57,580 --> 00:36:59,600
 Ja večeras imam zadovojstvo

1048
00:36:59,600 --> 00:37:01,600
 da postravim Juru,

1049
00:37:01,600 --> 00:37:03,900
 jelač koji je sa nama ovdje u studiju.

1050
00:37:03,900 --> 00:37:06,380
 Njega sam pozao za mladića

1051
00:37:06,380 --> 00:37:07,600
 koji redovito dolazi

1052
00:37:07,600 --> 00:37:09,120
 na duhovno-duhovite večeri

1053
00:37:09,120 --> 00:37:10,080
 na Svetom Duhu.

1054
00:37:10,080 --> 00:37:11,080
 Za one koji ne znaju,

1055
00:37:11,080 --> 00:37:12,360
 to su susjeti za mlade

1056
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:13,980
 koji krećujem u ovoga četvrtka

1057
00:37:13,980 --> 00:37:17,380
 i naša događanja su

1058
00:37:17,380 --> 00:37:17,980
 uglavnom

1059
00:37:17,980 --> 00:37:19,060
 okupljanje

1060
00:37:19,060 --> 00:37:19,980
 oko sakramenata,

1061
00:37:19,980 --> 00:37:20,660
 oko Isusa

1062
00:37:20,660 --> 00:37:21,240
 o presvetom

1063
00:37:21,240 --> 00:37:22,420
 oltarskom sakramentu.

1064
00:37:22,420 --> 00:37:23,300
 Jure,

1065
00:37:23,300 --> 00:37:24,300
 dobro nam došao,

1066
00:37:24,300 --> 00:37:25,360
 Bog te blagoslovio

1067
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:26,220
 i jako mi je drago

1068
00:37:26,220 --> 00:37:27,080
 da te večeras vidim

1069
00:37:27,080 --> 00:37:27,920
 ovdje u sudiju.

1070
00:37:28,140 --> 00:37:29,660
 Hvala vama na gostopremstvo.

1071
00:37:29,660 --> 00:37:30,640
 Dragi Jure,

1072
00:37:30,640 --> 00:37:33,180
 evo ti koji si u ovome vremenu,

1073
00:37:33,180 --> 00:37:34,140
 u ovome razdoblju

1074
00:37:34,140 --> 00:37:34,880
 gdje vjerujem,

1075
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:36,180
 sigurno nisi od uvijek

1076
00:37:36,180 --> 00:37:37,780
 bio onako,

1077
00:37:37,780 --> 00:37:38,360
 ajmo reći,

1078
00:37:38,360 --> 00:37:39,200
 blizu crkve,

1079
00:37:39,200 --> 00:37:39,880
 blizu vjere.

1080
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:40,820
 Možda si s vremenom

1081
00:37:40,820 --> 00:37:41,680
 otkrivao

1082
00:37:41,680 --> 00:37:44,620
 taj duhovni rast.

1083
00:37:44,620 --> 00:37:46,400
 Ti se slušao ono što sam govorio.

1084
00:37:46,400 --> 00:37:47,880
 Jesi li se negdje pronašao?

1085
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:48,480
 Pa ja,

1086
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:49,640
 po priličnom svemu.

1087
00:37:49,640 --> 00:37:51,500
 Da pa će,

1088
00:37:51,500 --> 00:37:54,180
 ne da nisam bio blizu crkve,

1089
00:37:54,180 --> 00:37:55,380
 vjere, sakramenata,

1090
00:37:55,380 --> 00:37:56,440
 baš naprotiv,

1091
00:37:56,520 --> 00:37:57,860
 bio sam totalno suprotno,

1092
00:37:57,860 --> 00:37:58,920
 živio sam totalno

1093
00:37:58,920 --> 00:37:59,800
 jedan drugi život

1094
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:01,560
 i baš kao i svet je Franjo,

1095
00:38:01,560 --> 00:38:03,100
 zapao sam u jednom depresiju bio.

1096
00:38:03,100 --> 00:38:05,100
 Nisam znao ni tko sam,

1097
00:38:05,100 --> 00:38:05,580
 ni šta sam,

1098
00:38:05,580 --> 00:38:06,300
 ni kud idem,

1099
00:38:06,300 --> 00:38:07,780
 ali mi se nije dalo ništa

1100
00:38:07,780 --> 00:38:09,280
 po tom pitanju poduzeti,

1101
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:10,940
 a pogotovo krenuti u crkvu

1102
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:12,680
 ili pomisliti nešto na taj način.

1103
00:38:12,680 --> 00:38:16,200
 Uz sakramenat klanjanja

1104
00:38:16,200 --> 00:38:18,040
 sam doživio braćenje.

1105
00:38:18,040 --> 00:38:18,740
 Dakle,

1106
00:38:18,740 --> 00:38:21,400
 prvi put sam nešto doživio u crkvi.

1107
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:22,660
 Da mi se nešto dogodilo,

1108
00:38:22,660 --> 00:38:23,740
 da me nešto dotaknulo,

1109
00:38:23,740 --> 00:38:24,420
 da mi je...

1110
00:38:24,420 --> 00:38:25,500
 Ma bilo kakva reakcija,

1111
00:38:25,500 --> 00:38:27,060
 to mi je uz klanjanje mi

1112
00:38:27,060 --> 00:38:28,300
 se dogodila prva reakcija.

1113
00:38:28,300 --> 00:38:30,460
 Nakon tog sam još jedan period

1114
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:32,600
 mislio da sam se baš obratio,

1115
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:34,100
 to je bio početak obratenja.

1116
00:38:34,100 --> 00:38:36,440
 Nakon tog sam mislio da sam se obratio,

1117
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:41,360
 i dalje je u meni vladalo ono nešto

1118
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:42,420
 da sam stalno pitao,

1119
00:38:42,420 --> 00:38:42,840
 pa Bože,

1120
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:43,920
 tu sam krenuo,

1121
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:44,660
 sam došao sam,

1122
00:38:44,660 --> 00:38:45,460
 ti ništa ne mijenja.

1123
00:38:45,460 --> 00:38:47,260
 Ja se i dalje osjećam isto.

1124
00:38:47,260 --> 00:38:50,440
 Do duhovitih večeri

1125
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:51,760
 na Svetom Duhu,

1126
00:38:51,760 --> 00:38:54,320
 tamo sam uz klanjanje

1127
00:38:54,320 --> 00:38:56,520
 stvarno upozno živog Isusa.

1128
00:38:57,320 --> 00:39:00,080
 gdje sam kroz etape,

1129
00:39:00,080 --> 00:39:02,580
 jedna od etapa je bila stvarno

1130
00:39:02,580 --> 00:39:03,760
 upraštenje samom sebi.

1131
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:05,600
 Dugo, dugo nisam znao

1132
00:39:05,600 --> 00:39:06,660
 uprostiti sam sebi

1133
00:39:06,660 --> 00:39:09,260
 i to se dosta odražavalo na mene,

1134
00:39:09,260 --> 00:39:09,880
 na moj život,

1135
00:39:09,880 --> 00:39:11,420
 na moje reakcije prema drugima,

1136
00:39:11,420 --> 00:39:12,840
 na moje ponašanje.

1137
00:39:14,080 --> 00:39:14,960
 kako sam sam sebi

1138
00:39:14,960 --> 00:39:15,960
 uspio uprostiti,

1139
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:17,580
 tako je stvarno krenuo

1140
00:39:17,580 --> 00:39:18,900
 na moj život Isusom,

1141
00:39:18,900 --> 00:39:19,680
 kako bi se reklo,

1142
00:39:19,680 --> 00:39:20,580
 full gasu.

1143
00:39:20,580 --> 00:39:22,160
 Nije bilo više stajanja.

1144
00:39:22,160 --> 00:39:23,460
 Znači, kad smo krenuli,

1145
00:39:23,460 --> 00:39:24,520
 krenulo je

1146
00:39:24,520 --> 00:39:27,160
 i evo stalno i tražim način

1147
00:39:27,160 --> 00:39:28,780
 kako svoj duhovni život

1148
00:39:28,780 --> 00:39:30,140
 dići na jednu višu razinu.

1149
00:39:30,140 --> 00:39:32,520
 Svakako uz sakramente,

1150
00:39:32,520 --> 00:39:34,100
 uz klanjanje Svetomisu,

1151
00:39:34,100 --> 00:39:35,020
 konstantnu ispovijed.

1152
00:39:35,020 --> 00:39:36,400
 To si dobro rekao.

1153
00:39:36,400 --> 00:39:38,320
 U nedelju smo sada slušali

1154
00:39:38,320 --> 00:39:39,160
 u prvom čitanju

1155
00:39:39,160 --> 00:39:40,240
 prorok Izaija kaže

1156
00:39:40,240 --> 00:39:42,640
 tražite Boga dok se može naći,

1157
00:39:42,740 --> 00:39:45,040
 zovite ga dok vas čuje.

1158
00:39:45,040 --> 00:39:48,140
 Gdje danas čovjek može tražiti Boga

1159
00:39:48,140 --> 00:39:49,940
 nego u sakramentima?

1160
00:39:49,940 --> 00:39:53,720
 Pa, za početak jedino samo u sakramentima.

1161
00:39:53,720 --> 00:39:55,800
 Ali evo, nažalost,

1162
00:39:55,800 --> 00:39:58,160
 ja dosta ti dolaziš na moje susete,

1163
00:39:58,160 --> 00:39:59,200
 znaš da često govorim

1164
00:39:59,200 --> 00:40:00,500
 o važnosti sakramenata,

1165
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:02,500
 ali često puta mladi misle

1166
00:40:02,500 --> 00:40:04,480
 evo upravo ga traži na krivim mjestima,

1167
00:40:04,480 --> 00:40:06,260
 a odbacuju sakramente.

1168
00:40:06,260 --> 00:40:08,340
 A Bog je upravo tamo koji nas čeka.

1169
00:40:08,340 --> 00:40:09,760
 Da, definitivno.

1170
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:11,140
 I preporučao bi svima mladima

1171
00:40:11,140 --> 00:40:12,860
 da su uopće ne srame doći.

1172
00:40:12,860 --> 00:40:14,260
 Ako imaju možda mišljenje

1173
00:40:14,260 --> 00:40:15,200
 da nisu dostani,

1174
00:40:15,200 --> 00:40:16,820
 da će ih neko tamo kritizirati

1175
00:40:16,820 --> 00:40:17,380
 ili nešto,

1176
00:40:17,380 --> 00:40:18,860
 ja sam se tako prvi put osjećao

1177
00:40:18,860 --> 00:40:19,640
 kad sam dolazio.

1178
00:40:19,640 --> 00:40:21,540
 Mislio sam da nisam vrijedan

1179
00:40:21,540 --> 00:40:22,620
 niti Isusa,

1180
00:40:22,620 --> 00:40:24,220
 niti tog društva

1181
00:40:24,220 --> 00:40:25,200
 koje se tamo okuplja,

1182
00:40:25,200 --> 00:40:26,340
 ljudi koji su u vjeri,

1183
00:40:26,340 --> 00:40:27,660
 ali baš suprotno.

1184
00:40:27,660 --> 00:40:29,540
 Ti ljudi su prvi

1185
00:40:29,540 --> 00:40:30,420
 koji će ti prvi,

1186
00:40:30,540 --> 00:40:31,840
 znači neće uopće gledati

1187
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:32,660
 tvoje loše strane.

1188
00:40:32,660 --> 00:40:33,540
 Prihvatit će te,

1189
00:40:33,540 --> 00:40:35,460
 pokušat će ti pomoć

1190
00:40:35,460 --> 00:40:37,000
 i definitivno tamo možeš

1191
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:38,500
 naći samo na odobravljavanje,

1192
00:40:38,500 --> 00:40:39,580
 a ne na osuđivanje.

1193
00:40:39,580 --> 00:40:41,260
 Tako da bih stvarno preporučao

1194
00:40:41,260 --> 00:40:42,460
 svim mladima da dođu,

1195
00:40:42,460 --> 00:40:43,000
 nek vide

1196
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:45,120
 i garantiram da će im se svidjeti.

1197
00:40:45,700 --> 00:40:47,540
 Kada pričaš o sebi

1198
00:40:47,540 --> 00:40:49,160
 i o prihvaćanju sebe,

1199
00:40:49,160 --> 00:40:50,320
 o duhovnom rastu,

1200
00:40:50,320 --> 00:40:52,020
 zasigurno su to oni

1201
00:40:52,020 --> 00:40:52,940
 prvi koraci,

1202
00:40:52,940 --> 00:40:53,760
 možda najvažniji

1203
00:40:53,760 --> 00:40:55,060
 da čovjek prihvati sebe,

1204
00:40:55,060 --> 00:40:56,900
 na se Bog stvori ovake kakve jesmo,

1205
00:40:56,900 --> 00:40:58,440
 voli nas svake kakve jesmo.

1206
00:40:58,440 --> 00:41:00,780
 Što bi možda istaknuo

1207
00:41:00,780 --> 00:41:02,380
 važno još u tom nekom

1208
00:41:02,380 --> 00:41:03,600
 duhovnom rastu?

1209
00:41:03,600 --> 00:41:04,440
 Kako zapravo

1210
00:41:04,440 --> 00:41:05,680
 kada čovjek i doživi

1211
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:07,440
 neko obraćenje ili rast,

1212
00:41:07,440 --> 00:41:09,220
 kako ostati u toj milosti?

1213
00:41:09,220 --> 00:41:11,120
 Ili možda imaš neku

1214
00:41:11,120 --> 00:41:12,000
 posebnu molitvu,

1215
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:13,800
 kako mladi mene često znaju pitam,

1216
00:41:14,140 --> 00:41:16,520
 slati poruku za određene životne situacije

1217
00:41:16,520 --> 00:41:17,780
 kad prekinu s nekim,

1218
00:41:17,780 --> 00:41:20,440
 onda pitaju patr šta moliti u ovom trenutku?

1219
00:41:20,440 --> 00:41:21,660
 Nemam, nemam ništa

1220
00:41:21,660 --> 00:41:23,220
 za posebne situacije,

1221
00:41:23,220 --> 00:41:24,600
 ali to je uopćenito molita.

1222
00:41:24,600 --> 00:41:25,960
 Dakle, svakodnevna molita.

1223
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:27,760
 Uz to čitanje Svjetog pisma

1224
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:29,960
 i redovito pohađanje Svete misle.

1225
00:41:29,960 --> 00:41:31,320
 Gdje se meni sad u ovom slučaju

1226
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:32,540
 dogodilo da ja svakodnevno

1227
00:41:32,540 --> 00:41:33,920
 pohađam Svjetu mislu.

1228
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:35,900
 Ali nisam samo na nedeljnih mislama.

1229
00:41:35,900 --> 00:41:37,500
 A reci mi evo,

1230
00:41:37,500 --> 00:41:39,720
 kada doživimo Boga,

1231
00:41:39,720 --> 00:41:41,500
 kada imamo iskustvo živoga Boga,

1232
00:41:41,660 --> 00:41:43,620
 onda to ne možemo čuvati samo za sebe.

1233
00:41:43,620 --> 00:41:45,320
 Osobno te poznajem

1234
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:47,420
 i znam koliko si ljudi mladih

1235
00:41:47,420 --> 00:41:48,740
 doveo tamo na Svjeti duh.

1236
00:41:48,740 --> 00:41:49,820
 Ti si zapravo,

1237
00:41:49,820 --> 00:41:51,440
 ja bih rekao poput Svjetog Franja,

1238
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:52,860
 dobio i svoje poslanje,

1239
00:41:52,860 --> 00:41:54,140
 a to je da evangeliziraš.

1240
00:41:54,140 --> 00:41:56,100
 Dosta si u tome dobar.

1241
00:41:56,100 --> 00:41:57,560
 I što, evo,

1242
00:41:57,560 --> 00:41:59,180
 možeš reći drugima,

1243
00:41:59,180 --> 00:42:02,680
 jesi li doživio neku neugodnu situaciju

1244
00:42:02,680 --> 00:42:04,260
 ili možda da nam ispričaš

1245
00:42:04,260 --> 00:42:05,200
 neki lijepi događaje

1246
00:42:05,200 --> 00:42:06,040
 kad si nekog frenda,

1247
00:42:06,040 --> 00:42:07,320
